{"tid":1032484,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Chris Hemsworth出演Netflix新片 擔旗做摔角巨星\t「禿鷹賀根」","createTime":"2019-02-22T11:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T12:41:43.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75c967d6087046ee698c9275bedfa8d4853bab7e","tid":1032484,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"以Marvel超級英雄「雷神索爾」聞名於全球的 35 歲的澳洲男演員Chris Hemsworth，身高 190 公分的他也以一身健壯肌肉身材硬漢形象深植人心，自從 2011 年加盟Marvel電影宇宙以來，他一直都列於每年度「最性感男星」的榜單之上。不過現在他確定要接演Netflix 的傳記新片，這一次雷神索爾要詮釋的新對象居然是美國傳奇摔角選手Hulk Hogan。<br />\n<br />\n即使你不熟悉摔角界，但你肯定在某個時刻看過Hulk Hogan下面這一張招牌的撕衣動作。身高 201 公分、體重 137 公斤的他體型有如縮小版的變形俠醫，他在摔角台上的知名必殺技有Axe Bomber和Running Lego Drop，他曾經用Axe Bomber將日本著名摔角選手安東尼奧豬木當場打昏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5c6e4a8d87511_14331564905c6e925cdbe74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F5c6e4a8d87511_14331564905c6e925cdbe74.jpg&h=85533e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於許多摔角迷來說，Hulk Hogan可以說是最能夠代表美國摔角運動的傳奇巨星。為了詮釋出他那一身緊實又充滿爆發戲劇性的筋肉體格，Netflix 才決定找來傳說中「大隻到後期要將肌肉Tune細」的荷里活一線猛男Chris Hemsworth飾演。"},{"pid":"05f19a07c9d3ebc0a78e566414f5291fc9b1a781","tid":1032484,"uid":232077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"伏筆？"},{"pid":"79462d2c6ac81114aae06320fdfd60c17dc06ab5","tid":1032484,"uid":160062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img1.looper.com/img/gallery/how-thor-ragnarok-radically-changed-the-mcu-and-no-one-seemed-to-notice/intro-1520358837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.looper.com%2Fimg%2Fgallery%2Fhow-thor-ragnarok-radically-changed-the-mcu-and-no-one-seemed-to-notice%2Fintro-1520358837.jpg&h=92b28c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n=<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2018/5/17/19fdcf46-db4b-4251-9214-85eb8c